Marquise Wilson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marquise_Wilson 0 Marquise Wilson is an American actor . He is best known for his role as Tyler Foster on the 1990s sitcom Hangin' with Mr. Cooper. He also co-starred in the 1994 film Sugar Hill, playing the young version Wesley Snipes' character. His other television credits include NYPD Blue, A Different World, Touched by an Angel, The Wild Thornberrys, Boomtown and Six Feet Under. He had a role in the 2004 direct-to-video film Slammed.
